trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: EditorZoneDesigner provides design-time rendering of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> controls.
trans-unit.target: EditorZoneDesigner gir utformingen gjengivelse av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: It includes support for editable designer regions, templates, and auto-formats to allow a page developer to easily alter the appearance of the control.
trans-unit.target: Det har støtte for redigerbare designer områder, maler og automatisk-formater for å tillate utvikler siden til å endre enkelt utseendet til kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The public <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collections provide quick formatting options for the page developer and can be safely overridden to change the default appearance of a custom control.
trans-unit.target: Offentligheten <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>samlinger gir rask formateringsalternativer for side-utviklere og trygt kan overstyres for å endre standardvisningen av en egendefinert kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner.AutoFormats%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of predefined automatic formatting schemes to display in the **Auto Format** dialog box for the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter samling av forhåndsdefinerte automatisk formatering skjemaene skal vises i den **automatisk Format** dialogboksen for den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The AutoFormats property overrides its base implementation to return a collection for use with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> controls.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Autoformater overstyrer base implementeringen for å returnere en samling for bruk med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: A pre-specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> with a default EditorZone scheme.
trans-unit.target: En forhåndsdefinerte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> med et standard EditorZone oppsett.

trans-unit.source: Invokes <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A?displayProperty=fullName> with a null parameter.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A?displayProperty=fullName> med en null-parameter.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the markup of the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som representerer markup kontrollens under utformingen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref>, if any, associated with the control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"> </xref>, hvis eventuelle tilknyttet kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the markup of the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som representerer markup kontrollens under utformingen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the content for the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter innholdet for den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the persisted form of the designer region's content.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som representerer faste formatet designer områdets innhold.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup to represent an empty control.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup til å representere en tom kontroll.

trans-unit.source: An empty <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: En tom <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Binding designer til det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"></xref> control associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"> </xref> tilknyttet designer.

trans-unit.source: Sets the content of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Angir innholdet i den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the content to go in the specified region.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som representerer innholdet gå i det angitte området.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups, each containing one or more template definitions.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av malen grupper, hver med ett eller flere malen definisjoner.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property overrides its base implementation to return a collection for use with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> controls.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups overstyrer base implementeringen for å returnere en samling for bruk med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: A pre-specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"></xref> with default settings for an EditorZone environment.
trans-unit.target: En forhåndsdefinerte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"> </xref> med standardinnstillinger for en EditorZone-miljøet.
